snippet.title: Townseek - Official PC Release Window Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Take a tour of the colorful world of Townseek, see trading elements, meet your companions, and embark on an adventure to discover new towns and more in this latest trailer for the upcoming exploration-trading game. Townseek will be available on PC in early 2024.

#GameTrailers #SoG #Gaming
